Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(part-a)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是From Beyond的Beyond Flamenco
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.02,0:01:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么情况？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(640,372)}虚偽的正義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:01:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没有弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.42,0:02:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快现出原形来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.28,0:02:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别按照字面意思理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是说我们是真正的兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我们的关系和兄弟极其相似
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么和我长得一样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别自说自话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来 是你长得和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.34,0:02:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是正 我是邪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.93,0:02:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说最容易理解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你为什么自称弗拉明戈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候你就会明白的 到时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.64,0:02:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事之后再问你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是领队吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.72,0:02:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停止装置 并让所有人投降！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我说倒是无所谓 但是我觉得不会有人听的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是个窗口罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗口？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,65000个From Beyond的集体意见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不过是集体意识的代言人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战败之后就变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.05,0:03:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说 我自己也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征服世界之后要怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何统治？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭六万多人根本对付不了六十亿人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界和平也同理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要人类还是人类 任何理由都能引起战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.21,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些话你都听烦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.21,0:03:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为这种不可能得到的东西而战是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的…这么想了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生这种念头的瞬间 就变成这个样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你还有那些家伙所做的事都毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同之处就是为何疯狂 如何疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疯狂到什么地步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.18,0:04:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 这个阶段很快就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经放弃这个世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也迟早会被人打败吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难听的话我就不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全听不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一能说的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我是自己想要保护大家才去保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是自己想要保护日本才去保护日本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意义之后再去想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的理由对这种荒谬的战斗而言恰到好处
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想做所以去做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们发动攻击的原因说到底也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能说出来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红斧战士 这究竟是怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道 但是危机还没有散去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamenger 回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.20,0:05:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond Flamenco自杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 日本毁灭装置仍在运作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我现在立刻安排拆除小队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来不及了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样装置就会到达地脉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我去申请轰炸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们快去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:05:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个方法了 要先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为这方法的成功率是最高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去吧 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.56,0:06:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 你们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamenger 拯救日本吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 接下来要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Robo 所有装置解放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏它！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Impact！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Kick！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Knee Drop！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…切腹先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经被消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以放市民们出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您接下来要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去富士山脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为同伴们正在那里等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:07:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 如果其中有一位叫武士…Flamen Red的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我向他转达一句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去转达吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是生还者的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介错号 GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 快给我说明情况！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 Flamenger正在阻止日本毁灭装置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们停手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会请美军进行轰炸！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样可能就来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总指挥是我 快服从命令！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.33,0:07:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒我直言 总理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果您现在要阻止Flamenger 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.39,0:07:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们是不会袖手旁观的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？你什么意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个出故障了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能听到杂音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:07:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Elbow！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洞穴也正在崩塌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会被活埋的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果不在这里阻止它 会到达熔岩层的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点就可以收拾掉这个庞然大物了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下那一招了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个太消耗能量了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那么做了 我们就无法从这些沙土和瓦砾中脱身了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是关键时刻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Drill！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻头就要用钻头来对付！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamenger！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就猜到会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rocket Punch？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,F Flamenger！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失礼啊 我的逃脱计划是不会有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 Flamen Robo…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\shad0\bord3\c&H443425&\3c&HC6C0AF&}谢谢你们给我们带来了和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\shad0\fs32\c&H595040&\3c&HB3A898&}内阁府 全国英雄联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那么 你为什么自称弗拉明戈」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「到时候你就会明白的 到时候」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗拉明戈武士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从美国来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Justice
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.…Justice？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我漂洋过海来向你传达真相
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人和师父很像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是你的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间正义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖投降吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是来找我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么拿枪对着我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许提问！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五秒之内双手抱头！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候 正义的英雄有几种应对方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A 乖乖投降 为自己辩解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.96,0:12:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B 拒绝投降 走为上计
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定是误会 所以我选择A
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是种正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我会选择B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种上来就要打架的态度是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说No的时候就要坚决说No
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的开枪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说对方是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是公安的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公安？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}注：警察组织中主要负责处理威胁国家体制的事态的部门 工作一般具有保密性质
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么公务员会来找我麻烦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚刚说过吧 你被骗了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我会突破他们逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也跟着我来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice Justice
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你就在这儿等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去教训教训他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们会开枪的 很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这比纽约的十字路口安全多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bad Justice！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Tackle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Tackle！Tackle！Tackle！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好强…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 趁现在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你应该有很多疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这些还是在秘密基地里慢慢聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.76,0:13:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 逃走是我们的首要任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 这拖车最好还是涂得朴素点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着歌整理整理心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平 平静不下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道大家有没有事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.07,0:14:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接电话？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是接不了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复 我们已经把逃亡中的Flamenger困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求支援！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他们赤手空拳也这么难对付…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为一个专业人士 身后也要防范呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩护得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我们可是拯救了日本吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 为什么我们会突然被公安的人袭击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.68,0:14:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全摸不着头脑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能联系上领队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.15,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话和短信都还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信网已经被完全切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样看来 领队那边也不好过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团体客人来了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人数太不科学了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下没辙了 认栽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 逮捕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 还少一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青岛苍一不在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 青岛在哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们突然被包围 逃得匆忙 哪顾得上那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.90,0:15:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道在这里肯定等得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.46,0:15:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要问总理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像是Flamen…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flamen Blue！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是有这么个团体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们应该解散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.34,0:16:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这打扮是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏有同伴们引开追兵 我才能潜入基地变身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 放下吧放下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得有亲爱的国民来拜访我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我单独和他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 那边那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在的支持率如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前是72%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,72%吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总理 如果你不能给出令人信服的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你是总理大臣 我也不会手下留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要抓我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这副来打架的气势可真让人遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次想来见我的时候 记得先预约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 没想到…会 会是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在担心Flamenger的同伴们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看新闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能会震惊 但这样也能知道同伴们的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自导自演真是惊人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.75,0:17:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑人已经接连…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条临时新闻令社会…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放临时新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临时新闻？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(634,502)}Flamenger有颠覆国家罪的嫌疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个月来所发生的From Beyond恐怖袭击事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑为Flamenger小队的自导自演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs32\pos(634,502)}被逮捕的长官 要丈治嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师 师父！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\shad0\3c&H705A5C&\c&HFBFEDA&\pos(548,289)}嫌疑人团伙Flamenger所潜伏的工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该团伙与扮演敌方组织的From Beyond相互勾结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,580)\c&HFBFEDA&\bord4\shad0\3c&H705A5C&}被逮捕的Flamenger一行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引发众多事件 扰乱社会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.41,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察已经逮捕Flamenger团伙的嫌疑人并听取口供
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于政府在其中的牵涉 稍后奥崎总理将召开见面会说明
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是胡编乱造！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是胡编乱造 如果大众都相信就会变成真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传媒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵From Beyond的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是日本政府！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太扯了 他们为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.09,0:18:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了利用一次危机来统一民意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让政局变得有利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上 这几个月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于你们的活跃 内阁支持率上升
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多法案都通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们利用了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的国家也发生了同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括越南 伊拉克在内 国家想要转移民众视线的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会让我和怪物 异形和宇宙人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义先生也是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这一切都是好莱坞的编剧和工作室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.67,0:19:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受政府委托而创作的虚构事件！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他们犯了一个错误
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你们太过正义了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了太多民众的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越了英雄 成为了领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 你们可能会成为政府无法掌控的麻烦人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时他们会做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认到嫌疑人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是 人更多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧 弗拉明戈武士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.76,0:19:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没弱到会在这儿挂掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来到了游乐场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让你们体验体验我的英雄秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.10,0:19:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Home Run！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:19:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Justice Beam！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beam！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Beam！Beam！Beam！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的Police真是太孱弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上都要吃大量谷物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有大块肉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用麻醉枪 真是不解风情…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一连串事件都是沉迷虚拟作品的羽佐间正义为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经过周密策划 自导自演的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.43,0:20:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与政府完全无关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家请看这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.00,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs45\pos(288,544)\frz356.287\3c&HFAF0E2&\c&H2C281E&}从羽佐间正义　　　\N家中所没收的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.00,phone,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs40\frz356.287\3c&HFAF0E2&\c&H2C281E&\pos(722,614)}与同谋的　\NBeyond Flamenco　　\N接触的羽佐间正义\h\h\h
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很异常
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs32\bord1\3c&HC3DBE5&\pos(404,378)}弗拉明戈武士\N策劃書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.01,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b0\fs32\3c&HC3DBE5&\frz357.484\pos(698,378)}弗拉明戈武士\N構思集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次可大事不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了防范此类事件再次发生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们提出了非认可正义活动限制法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现已进入审议阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 本着将国民安全作为第一考量的宗旨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:20:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分可疑人物均已被捕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未落网的只有羽佐间正义
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.71,0:21:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本国将对他进行全国通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在这！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降吧 弗拉明戈武士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.94,0:21:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是日本的敌人！
Comment: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(ED2)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:25.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话筒对面熟悉的嗓音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.30,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听上去还算精神 让我松了口气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:33.27,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月台挥手道别之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.76,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记不清已有多久无缘相聚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.87,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上双眼的夜航
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:44.07,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像往常那样在月亮背面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.98,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相约在23点碰头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:55.95,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不远万里也要与你相见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.80,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以往读过的圣埃克絮佩里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:03.74,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定漏掉了重要的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.58,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心里确实存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:11.49,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:15.15,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起头来笑一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:19.45,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,静静仰望同一片夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:25.81,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从未分离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:33.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:41.17,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从未分离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:48.22,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们并不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:25.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受話器の向こう　聴き慣れた声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.30,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元気そうでほっとしたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:33.27,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会えなくなってどれくらいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.76,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手を振ったホーム
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.87,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目を閉じ夜間飛行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:44.07,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもの月の裏で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.98,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23時　待ち合わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.12,0:21:55.95,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな遠くても君と出逢える
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:59.80,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昔読んだサンテグジュペリ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.89,0:22:03.74,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと肝心なことは見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.96,0:22:07.58,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心の中　確かにいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:11.49,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いろんな表情をした君が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:11.49,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(625,630)}かお
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:15.15,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俯かないで笑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:19.45,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと同じ夜空を見上げながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:19.45,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(610,630)}そら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:25.81,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離れ離れじゃないね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.38,0:22:33.60,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しくなんかないね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:41.17,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離れ離れじゃないね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:48.22,ED2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂しくなんかないね
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(epilogo)
Comment: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(trailer)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:51.09,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(272,608)}流浪的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样 总理居然背叛了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.65,0:22:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是羽佐间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.82,0:22:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟 弗拉明戈武士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.59,0:22:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总理？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个报道是怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想说那些的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是官房长官拜托我一定要说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.61,0:23:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.58,0:23:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会详细跟你解释的 你能到我官邸来一趟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 我在中野坂上…不不不 我不会上当的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs36}注：东京都中野区地名
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.23,0:23:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀 真亏你能发觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.96,0:23:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗！别耍我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就把我的藏品 切腹零食怪人卡全套送给你当奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？虽然我已经有了但是还是好想要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我这就带过去 你在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中野坂上二丁目的…不不不 都说了我不会上当的！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.51,0:23:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是警察…我要挂了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会再打给你的
